<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Campus Life | BU</title>

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial;}
body{background:#1a102c;}

/* HERO */
.hero{
height:40vh;
background:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523580846011-d3a5bc25702b?w=1920') center/cover;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
color:white;
}

/* CONTAINER */
.container{
max-width:1100px;
margin:50px auto;
display:flex;
gap:40px;
padding:20px;
}

/* IMAGE */
.image img{
width:100%;
border-radius:10px;
}

/* CONTENT */
.card{
background:white;
padding:30px;
border-radius:10px;
}

.card h2{margin-bottom:10px;}
.card p{margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1.6;color:#555;}

@media(max-width:768px){
.container{flex-direction:column;}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="hero">
<h1>Campus Life</h1>
</div>

<div class="container">

<div class="image">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509062522246-3755977927d7?w=800">
</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>Life at :contentReference</h2>

<p>
Campus life is vibrant and full of opportunities for students to grow and enjoy.
</p>

<p>
Students participate in cultural events, technical fests, sports, and clubs.
</p>

<p>
The campus provides hostels, sports facilities, libraries, and recreational areas.
</p>

<p>
Activities like dance, music, competitions, and workshops help build confidence.
</p>

<p>
It creates a balance between academic learning and personal development.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>